James McCaffrey (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/James_McCaffrey_(actor) 0 James McCaffrey is a Northern Irish–American actor, born in Belfast, known for his role as Max Payne in the Max Payne video game series. He has also had main roles and recurring roles in a number of television series as well as appearing in feature films.
